			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">BASIC CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Move club -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad</font>		
                  <br>&nbsp; Select action -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Adjusts the angle of the cue on the ball for spins -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button + D-Pad</font>				
                  <br>&nbsp; Adjusts the angle on the ball to add back spin or to jump the ball -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle Button + D-Pad</font>	
                  <br>&nbsp; Cancel action -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle Button</font>	
                  <br>&nbsp; Zoom in and out -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L1 or R1 Button</font>	
                  <br>&nbsp; Displays each balls number -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L2 Button</font>	
                  <br>&nbsp; Changes to free camera mode -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;R2 Button</font>	
                  <br>&nbsp; Pause game / Options menu -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br><br>	
				  &nbsp;</td>
